comment: Hayward (UTA) sets the screen on Jordan (LAC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Hayward (UTA) and Redick (LAC) briefly engage and separate away from the ball.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Redick (LAC) was behind the three-point line on his made shot was upheld.
Booker (UTA) makes incidental contact as Mbah a Moute (LAC) goes around the ball screen.

Jordan (LAC) grabs the ball on the shot attempt after it has touched the rim and is in the imaginary cylinder above the rim, and defensive goaltending is called. After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court was upheld.
Redick (LAC) makes incidental contact with Booker (UTA) prior to the inbound pass.
Ingles (UTA) commits a take foul on Redick (LAC).
Hood (UTA) commits a take foul on Redick (LAC).
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Ingles (UTA) was behind the three-point line on his made shot was overturned.
Booker (UTA) commits a take foul on Paul (LAC).
Hood (UTA) commits a take foul on Paul (LAC).
